globs: *.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

- Keep components as small as possible
- Separate UI from the business logic
- Extract utils from your components, so you can test those utils
- Always use Flowbite component, first search the corresponding component documentation there: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/themesberg/flowbite/refs/heads/main/llms.txt then create a component in the design-system-components folder
